      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>''There is credible evidence in the record to suggest that Microsoft, convinced of its innocence, continues to do business as it has in the past and may yet do to other markets what it has already done in the PC operating system and browser markets.''</p>
        <p>JUDGE THOMAS PENFIELD JACKSON. [C12]</p>
